{"tid":984730,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾掩埋咪錶位　畀錢考起司機　網民齊獻計！","createTime":"2019-01-17T04:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T09:33:30.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"666523757e522b92ea82dd73e225fb67a083b625","tid":984730,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"<strong>垃圾掩埋咪錶位　畀錢考起司機　網民齊獻計！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117103622840-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117103622840-0117_00822_001.html&d=UvKuUuc4QvHjzgPyDvtmW9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=290fd08f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117103622840-0117_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117103622840-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190117111144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117103622840-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190117111144&h=b15ed753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入個錶都咁難？<br />\n<br />\n香港向來錶位難求，惟近日有人在九龍城覓得空位，卻發現咪錶已被垃圾掩埋，笑言︰「想入錶都唔得」。<br />\n<br />\n網民星期三（16日）於Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」上傳兩張相片，可見在九龍城石鼓壟道近富豪東方酒店的一處露天泊車場，行人路堆滿建築廢料及垃圾，大包小包的麻包袋圍堵咪錶，司機難以接近。<br />\n<br />\n有網民獻計︰「用念力」、「有心做唔會做唔到，睇吓你自己想唔想做，只要有恒心，入錶可成真」。有人則警告有錶不入，隨時收牛肉乾︰「阿Sir仍然見到後面嘅紅燈閃吓閃吓」。"},{"pid":"9b4486aae263d59c6a135ec422972d4b156eb834","tid":984730,"uid":13495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"報驚叫啲狗嚟睇下囉"},{"pid":"588e797841e88fd1f810a1d16414d08e7a5dfca6","tid":984730,"uid":193893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"買多兩包泥頭堆埋個錶佢"},{"pid":"51e517228c6077d054e0029365e91a94dc59e040","tid":984730,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"冇衝突，阿SIR照告你，你告返放垃圾果個"},{"pid":"78f359bd889b3cdefd8944f504e2f60c1eeb491f","tid":984730,"uid":143849,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"你入唔到錶 姐係睇唔到啦<br />\n咁你睇唔到 呀sir又點睇你無入錶？<br />\n呀sir睇到你無入錶 姐係你應該入到錶啦"},{"pid":"3422fcec9aac1ca82421f5a226025be691d470d3","tid":984730,"uid":14073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78f359bd889b3cdefd8944f504e2f60c1eeb491f","tid":984730,"uid":143849,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"你入唔到錶 姐係睇唔到啦<br />\n咁你睇唔到 呀sir又點睇你無入錶？<br />\n呀sir睇到你無入錶 姐係你應該入到錶啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毅進仔雖然蠢，都唔使行埋去逐個錶睇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c3806f0d92375cb6dedd4c4b640111d3af967f","tid":984730,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f359bd889b3cdefd8944f504e2f60c1eeb491f","tid":984730,"uid":143849,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"你入唔到錶 姐係睇唔到啦<br />\n咁你睇唔到 呀sir又點睇你無入錶？<br />\n呀sir睇到你無入錶 姐係你應該入到錶啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"「阿Sir仍然見到後面嘅紅燈閃吓閃吓」"},{"pid":"9e5fce1ebce065f961de7c008757df96a90a5c81","tid":984730,"uid":232302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"78f359bd889b3cdefd8944f504e2f60c1eeb491f","tid":984730,"uid":143849,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"你入唔到錶 姐係睇唔到啦<br />\n咁你睇唔到 呀sir又點睇你無入錶？<br />\n呀sir睇到你無入錶 姐係你應該入到錶啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Rush out 7"},{"pid":"95c749c936a8399cedc70c09a69a9a25ec255b3c","tid":984730,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36c3806f0d92375cb6dedd4c4b640111d3af967f","tid":984730,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f359bd889b3cdefd8944f504e2f60c1eeb491f","tid":984730,"u